=======  FILES  =======

#dataMassager

    reading all the files, randomaly ordring the files as training and testing sets.
    by choosing 75 % of each name's tweets.


#parsing

    extract the features:
    hashtags,
    tags,
    links,
    emoji use,
    average tweet length
    spanish letters,
    common word use,
    shortest, longest word.

    building the word vector for each tweet by the following features and creating the data.


#ploting

    extract graphs of the basic data.
    average and variance for each feature.

#classifier

    gets an tweet and predict which name tweeeted it.